formElementBorderColorFocus.comment: Should be used for all form-elements when the component has active or focus state and it's needed to render border attribute, or combined with shadows.

formElementBorderColorError.comment: Should be used for all form-elements when the component has error state and it's needed to render border attribute, or combined with shadows.
